Third-party data
------------------------------------------------------------------------

tablet_db.json contains factual tablet parameters (model name, USB
vendor/product IDs, physical dimensions, maximum coordinate values,
maximum pressure, HID input report length, and report-parser family
names). These values are derived from the OpenTabletDriver configuration
database.

    OpenTabletDriver
    https://github.com/OpenTabletDriver/OpenTabletDriver
    Licensed under the GNU Lesser General Public License v3.0 (LGPL-3.0)

Only factual hardware parameters are reproduced; no OpenTabletDriver
source code is included or distributed in this project. To regenerate
tablet_db.json from an OpenTabletDriver checkout, run:

    python tools/import_otd_configs.py <path-to>/OpenTabletDriver.Configurations/Configurations
